Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.93,0:00:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛逝的秒針 劃過天際的彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.69,0:00:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在社會人心疲累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.47,0:00:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理是一劑良藥喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.54,0:00:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件是死神陣內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.47,0:00:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神出鬼沒的棘手罪犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.43,0:00:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.21,0:00:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.23,0:00:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.98,0:01:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神陣內殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.59,0:01:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我將取缺德律師黑田憲三的小命 死神陣內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺德律師黑田憲三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在來接你到地獄去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.91,0:02:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.95,0:02:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.84,0:02:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神陣內 新的挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.67,0:02:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人會在電影開始五分鐘之內就睡著嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.69,0:02:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好不容易抽中參加試映會 你卻一直在睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什麼辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.02,0:02:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是昨天晚上為了工作才熬到那麼晚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.31,0:02:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看是熬夜喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這部電影真的有點沉悶 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.67,0:03:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 可是我倒覺得很好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看這部影片演的還不就是那些老套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.55,0:03:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是飾演死神陣內的南條隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.40,0:03:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.94,0:03:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你就是名偵探毛利小五郎先生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.62,0:03:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我就是名偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是南條隼人的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失敬 這部電影還真是好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.62,0:03:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我有事情想跟您談談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利偵探 這邊請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這間辦公室還挺不錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.75,0:03:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.62,0:03:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還正愁找不到新的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.07,0:04:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里美小姐 這一位就是名偵探毛利小五郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.96,0:04:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是南條隼人的經紀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫吉野里美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里美 把那個拿來給毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳別管 去拿過來就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.07,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.06,0:04:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我將取南條隼人的小命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神陣內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是死神陣內送來的預告函
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是今天早上在郵筒裡找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情你們報警了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.17,0:04:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那個必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.95,0:04:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情一想就知道是惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.04,0:04:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 老公…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是對妳說過任性也要有個限度嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.49,0:04:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾位現在可以回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 南條先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.42,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南條太太可是為了你的安全在操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.15,0:04:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這封恐嚇信上面說的是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也可以保護我自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 我有很多事情要忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾位請回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野 妳今天也可以下班了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前在記者背後的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.34,0:05:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是日前接到死神陣內殺人預告函的電影演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南條隼人的辦公室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前時間是晚上九點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟死神陣內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.32,0:05:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會如預言現身嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.38,0:05:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 毛利小五郎先生也在現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以更叫人覺得緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.61,0:05:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.53,0:05:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是名偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.67,0:05:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.11,0:05:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這樣就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.88,0:05:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家先休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有問題的 南條太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這裏在我們這些人嚴密的戒備之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.04,0:05:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信那個壞傢伙是絕對不敢輕舉妄動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.52,0:05:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.37,0:05:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要這麼努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣死神陣內是不可能會出現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.52,0:06:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照我看這根本就是南條隼人為了宣傳電影搞的噱頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.20,0:06:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南條太太 妳冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買些飲料來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.45,0:06:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.44,0:06:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在那裡的人不就是經紀人里美小姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.92,0:06:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼還沒有回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.97,0:06:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在那裡幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.79,0:06:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許她想從那裡注意辦公室的狀況吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.44,0:06:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她一定也在為南條先生擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.44,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們走吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.60,0:06:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候還沒有離開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只剩下南條先生一個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大野導演呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才說要去一下洗手間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼會去那麼久呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去看看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.03,0:06:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.10,0:06:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神陣內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝影機 把攝影機移過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我束手就擒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.85,0:07:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 被他給跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.26,0:07:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 南條先生那邊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.13,0:07:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.56,0:07:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里美小姐 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我在那邊那間漢堡店的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.68,0:07:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就看見死神陣內跑到那棟大樓的裡面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.70,0:07:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.88,0:07:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 剛才那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 那個兇手現在還在七樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.90,0:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才看到影子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.88,0:07:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這個膠帶是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕緣膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.17,0:08:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來那個兇手就從現場消失了是不是 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.47,0:08:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的窗戶全部都從裡面鎖住了 打不開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要從七樓逃脫的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有利用電梯或是逃生樓梯才有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.83,0:08:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 問題是在我們趕到那裡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.48,0:08:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手已經不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.66,0:09:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們確定都沒有人離開這棟大樓嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為當時我們跟電視台的記者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一直待在這棟大樓的前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是逃生樓梯那邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.49,0:09:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.08,0:09:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果藉由這棟大樓的逃生樓梯到達一樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.37,0:09:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會被引導到電梯那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.82,0:09:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要出去 還是必須經過同一個出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.27,0:09:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有注意逃生樓梯那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是都沒有看到任何人走下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你們這麼說那個兇手就像煙霧一樣地消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.62,0:09:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不覺得很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個房間的燈被點亮的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.52,0:09:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個兇手明明就站在那個窗戶旁邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是日光燈的開關是在門口旁邊的牆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.53,0:09:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手到底是用什麼方法將房間的燈打開的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經你這麼一說還真是很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手在將南條先生殺害之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為了什麼要把房裡的日光燈打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.12,0:09:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.87,0:10:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過兇手到底為什麼會將這卷絕緣膠帶留在現場呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.18,0:10:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.26,0:10:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能是想讓我們趕到這裡的時候被這卷膠帶絆倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.48,0:10:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就可以為兇手製造脫逃的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.28,0:10:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是剛才被絆倒的人只有毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.91,0:10:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要求他確定稿子的傳真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.83,0:10:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十點零三分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.34,0:10:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是在南條先生被殺之前不久的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.79,0:10:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也正好是死神陣內出現在公園的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.05,0:10:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂碰現場的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.16,0:10:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是下個星期要發售的雜誌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刊登的一個訪問的原稿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.25,0:10:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南條先生今天留在公司就是為了等這份傳真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.17,0:10:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 剛才這個可疑的人在外面鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.28,0:10:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是什麼可疑的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大野先生 你剛才跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.06,0:10:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從洗手間出來就看不見大家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就一直在公園裡面找大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你殺了我先生吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等 妳在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.87,0:11:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 目前現場的所有關係人當中沒有不在場證明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.13,0:11:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像就只有你一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是為了三年前那個意外懷恨在心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會殺了我先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.73,0:11:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.98,0:11:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前的意外到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.12,0:11:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在雖然是娛樂節目的製作人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.38,0:11:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我原本是一位專拍電影的導演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.67,0:11:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前我在拍攝死神陣內電影的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了那件意外我就退出電影界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得那一天原本已經約好要拍片的替身人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.45,0:11:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等了很久始終沒有出現在現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 不用替身直接上好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以這樣 南條 這樣太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你辦得到吧 北野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過不久你就要成為主角了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點危險不算什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.76,0:11:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導演 我現在就可以演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.86,0:11:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.90,0:11:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後北野也答應自己上場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上南條態度強硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.96,0:12:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就硬著頭皮開拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有想到車子突然爆炸燒了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.93,0:12:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北野就這樣一去不回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.27,0:12:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就因此扛下所有的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.43,0:12:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辭去了導演的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.37,0:12:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對南條的確懷有恨意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.87,0:12:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還有一個人對他懷有更深的恨意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.42,0:12:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就在現場嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.89,0:12:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道里美從前跟北野是一對情侶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.07,0:12:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎 里美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.12,0:12:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確那個時候我跟北野是男女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.74,0:12:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他其實是隸屬同一家經紀公司的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個不怎麼出名的動作女演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.84,0:12:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 那是一件不幸的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.10,0:12:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我絕對沒有因為那件意外就懷恨南條先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.85,0:12:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…里美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.82,0:12:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在南條先生被殺的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.61,0:12:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直跟我們站在這棟大樓的前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我們剛才在公園裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好用攝影機拍下死神陣內的樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.31,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 那我們就看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.95,0:13:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六樓那裡就有一架放映機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我這就過去準備一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.97,0:13:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手為什麼要在公園裡面故意讓大家看到他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有剛才窗邊的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這其中一定有些特殊的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從下面傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.52,0:13:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是爬樓梯比較快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.67,0:13:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神陣內他出現了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.19,0:13:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.16,0:13:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 妳坐電梯到了六樓這裡以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.78,0:13:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將逃生出口的門打開的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本躲在辦公室的死神陣內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然對妳開了一槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.09,0:13:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後那傢伙就跑了 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.62,0:14:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從南條先生被殺到現在正好過了一個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.10,0:14:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是兇手在這段時間居然能夠躲過警方的注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.92,0:14:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直躲在這棟大樓裡沒有被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且兇手為什麼要對里美小姐開槍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時只有里美小姐一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其對她開槍引起警方的注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜地逃走應該更安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.28,0:14:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.51,0:14:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場的查驗工作已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.85,0:14:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有發現槍彈的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.54,0:14:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.51,0:14:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子彈很有可能從逃生口飛出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.86,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找到可就困難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.77,0:14:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.71,0:14:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可以開始播放錄影帶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.37,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就事不宜遲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.99,0:14:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有這卷帶子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.44,0:14:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶子還是溫溫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.54,0:14:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且根本都還沒有倒到最前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.35,0:14:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可不能隨便亂碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.29,0:15:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道兇手使用的手法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在證據還不夠充分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 剛才那份傳真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你要上哪去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我想的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.60,0:15:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就錯不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.87,0:15:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.74,0:15:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要在這裡到處亂晃行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.18,0:15:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你看這份傳真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.02,0:15:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是剛才的那份傳真嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.32,0:15:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪裡有問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.78,0:15:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.11,0:15:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.94,0:15:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.04,0:15:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.68,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 謎團解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.64,0:15:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實兇手根本就沒有從命案現場消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.08,0:15:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他從一開始就不在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.46,0:15:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.27,0:16:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們一群人沖進大樓裏之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.41,0:16:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南條先生早就已經被這個兇手給殺害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.85,0:16:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 柯南不是明明在七樓的窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到那個兇手的影子了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.37,0:16:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那只是兇手故意設計的一個詭計罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詭計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就可以示範給大家看一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你請所有的人到七樓這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.26,0:16:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外再請你幫我準備一卷絕緣膠帶跟一條釣線好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.07,0:16:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕緣膠帶和釣線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.24,0:16:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然大家都已經到齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就可以開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.81,0:16:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先這個兇手在將南條先生殺害之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.25,0:16:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就將房間裡的日光燈關掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.92,0:16:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用絕緣膠帶從窗戶的最下方開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.85,0:16:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點的貼出一個看上去像是人影的黑影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.40,0:16:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著再利用釣線將電梯內側的上方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.87,0:16:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟外側電梯門之間的空隙綁緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著再將這條釣線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.28,0:16:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉到辦公室裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日光燈的開關上繞上一圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著再將釣線拉到窗戶旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁住絕緣膠帶的紙圏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.90,0:17:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 不管是誰想要趕到這個現場來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.39,0:17:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一樓那裡按了電梯按鈕的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候 從外面往上看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.18,0:17:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶上面被絕緣膠布貼住的部分就會將室內光線擋住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從外面看起來就像一個人站在這裡一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.44,0:17:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著釣線被電梯往下拉之後就會將窗上的膠布撕下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來就像是一個人影消失的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候膠帶一直被電梯拉著跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.39,0:17:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到被電梯門擋住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.43,0:17:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後釣線斷了 膠帶就留在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那個時候的槍聲怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.61,0:17:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個槍聲是兇手事先錄在錄音帶上面的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錄音帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.19,0:17:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手利用裝了消音裝置的手槍先把南條先生殺害之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再完成剛才那一個電梯的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.61,0:17:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就利用逃生樓梯來到六樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.56,0:17:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那卷錄了槍聲的錄音帶放進錄放機裡播放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.54,0:18:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 從大樓的下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.30,0:18:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是分不清楚槍聲到底是從哪一樓發出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.41,0:18:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這卷錄有槍聲的錄音帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有前十五分鐘的空白部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.93,0:18:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就是利用這段空白的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.04,0:18:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扮成死神陣內的樣子出現在公園裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再將我們引到大樓前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.06,0:18:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後他再跟我們會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.42,0:18:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以替他製造出跟我們一起聽到槍聲的不在場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.98,0:18:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.95,0:18:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說兇手就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.89,0:18:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.85,0:18:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠設計這套手法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野里美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.52,0:18:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有妳一個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.55,0:18:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是第二聲槍聲的目的又是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那槍聲應該不在她的計畫之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.50,0:18:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為里美小姐沒有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.87,0:18:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動回播的按鍵並沒有取消掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.54,0:18:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她所使用的是六十分鐘的錄音帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.89,0:18:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要經過一小時 那聲槍響就會再出現一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.66,0:19:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候妳藉口說要準備放映機下去六樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是先將釣線給回收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候槍聲卻突然響了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.13,0:19:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚慌失措的妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.42,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌慌張張地將錄音帶藏了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.26,0:19:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們趕來的時候就隨口對我們撒了個謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據呢 你根本沒有證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要證據當然有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.90,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.07,0:19:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在請你看看那份傳真的稿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.07,0:19:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這份稿子裡面的其中一頁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.93,0:19:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面應該沾了一點痕跡才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為里美小姐正在行兇的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.49,0:19:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份傳真剛好正一頁一頁地傳進辦公室裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.89,0:19:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.75,0:19:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說沾有血跡的傳真上面開頭所標明的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.33,0:19:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是南條先生真正的死亡時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九點五十九分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.07,0:19:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家在大樓前面聽到槍聲的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在十點十五分的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.92,0:19:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實在那之前的十五分鐘 南條先生已經遇害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.28,0:19:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你剛才從柯南手中所拿走的那卷錄音帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面應該就錄有那重要的一聲槍聲才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.23,0:20:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且死神陣內當時出現在公園能敏捷地擺脫大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.00,0:20:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有是動作女演員出身的妳才能做得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是我殺了南條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.88,0:20:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是為了報復南條在三年前殺死廣之的這個仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.41,0:20:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那件事應該是個意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.03,0:20:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一開始也是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.47,0:20:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是後來有一天我看到廣之的一篇日記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.90,0:20:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外發生之前的那個星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.38,0:20:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人跟他說希望他能夠代替南條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.38,0:20:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接任第二代死神陣內的這個角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了查清楚他真正的死因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.17,0:20:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進入南條的公司當經紀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.45,0:20:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後大概在一個月前的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.11,0:20:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於聽到南條帶著酒氣得意洋洋地告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.14,0:20:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.71,0:20:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前在拍攝死神陣內那部電影的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.03,0:20:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了一個年輕人妳還記不記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.50,0:20:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得好像是因為沒有替身就開始拍片才發生的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.60,0:20:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.11,0:20:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告訴妳一件有趣的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.00,0:21:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那是我騙了那天的替身人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.35,0:21:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意告訴他那天拍攝的時候不要到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.12,0:21:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.41,0:21:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是個新人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.73,0:21:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然就妄想要把我飾演的角色搶過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道這是什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.76,0:21:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.85,0:21:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是固定越野車前輪零件最重要的鉚釘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.42,0:21:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼 那麼這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.09,0:21:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.96,0:21:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他根本就不是因為出了意外才死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是南條他親手殺死廣之的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.25,0:21:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以寄出預告函
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.71,0:21:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了利用媒體製造不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.24,0:21:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經對他說這麼一來可以同時為電影宣傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南條也就欣然答應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.98,0:21:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的全部都被你說中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.85,0:23:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次死神陣內對名偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.52,0:23:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子死神陣內是輸得一蹋糊塗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.94,0:23:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.11,0:23:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我毛利小五郎的字典裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.84,0:23:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有謎案這個名詞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.23,0:23:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是誰幫你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.76,0:23:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
